# 🏪 EasyReal - Sari-Sari Store & Household Dashboard

A highly intuitive, scannable Web interface crafted for local home-business owners (such as a mother managing a local retail micro-grocery store).

## 🗂️ File Layout Structure
Make sure these three files sit side-by-side inside the exact same project root folder:
```text
├── index.html
├── style.css
└── script.js